comments: Curry (GSW) receives the ball and takes more than two steps after his gather and prior to the release of his dribble.
Dinwiddie (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Curry (GSW) during the drive.
Bullock (DAL) makes marginal contact with Wiggins' (GSW) body during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (GSW) swipes down and legally dislodges the ball from Bullock (DAL).
Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Wiggins (GSW) and firms up to absorb the contact during the pick.
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes marginal contact with his forearm to the body of Wiggins (GSW) during the drive.
Doncic (DAL) avoids making contact with Curry's (GSW) arm during his shooting motion.
Curry (GSW) initiates contact with his off arm into Doncic (DAL) after the release of his shot near the rim.
Lee (GSW) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (DAL).
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Bullock (DAL) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Bullock (DAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Payton II (GSW) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Lee (GSW) does not inbound the ball in under 5 seconds.
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
